JSON Schema Validation
Suppose response:

{
   "id":101,
   "name":"Varsha",
   "email":"varsha@test.com"
}

Schema checks:
id → Integer
name → String
email → String
Required fields
No unexpected fields
Prompt:
Analyze this JSON response.
